# InsightAT – matches doc/design/02_coding_style.md and README
BasedOnStyle: LLVM
Language: Cpp
IndentWidth: 2
# doc/design/02_coding_style.md §6: 命名空间内容不额外缩进
NamespaceIndentation: None
ColumnLimit: 100
AccessModifierOffset: -2
AlignAfterOpenBracket: Align
AlignTrailingComments: true
BreakBeforeBraces: Attach
FixNamespaceComments: true
PointerAlignment: Left
SortIncludes: true
